I can only guess that `HEAD[epc]` is a literal slot name within your child component, eg

``` html
&lt;slot name=&quot;HEAD[epc]&quot; :label=&quot;label&quot; :field=&quot;field&quot;&gt;&lt;/slot&gt;
```

In order to use this, you will need to create a `data` or `computed` property to represent it and use the [dynamic slot name syntax][1]. For example, in your parent component

``` html
&lt;template v-slot:[slotname]=&quot;data&quot;&gt;
```

``` js
data: () =&gt; ({
  slotname: &#39;HEAD[epc]&#39;
})
```

