For your second question I suggest you to create a relation with a `Image` class where you can store all the image conversion you require. But this can be a little tricky and may require time to be coded. Fortunately there are tons of libraries that can handle this for you. My favourite is [Laravel medialibrary](https://docs.spatie.be/laravel-medialibrary/v7/introduction/)

